Test Environment for SBLIM Samba Instrumentation

The SBLIM project offers a Test Suite to perform tests against
the provider implementation and consistence tests against system
values.

Prerequisites 
.............

- sblim-cmpi-samba package propertly installed
- testsuite package


Pepare Test
...........

done automatically during configure


Install Configuration Files
...........................

done during make install


Run Test
........

Run the test in the testsuite directory (typically /usr/share/sblim-testsuite)
by executing 
. test-cmpi-samba.sh
echo Status: $SBLIM_TESTSUITE_RUN
